text:
Great selection of drinks! I've only tried the iced ones, which are definitely more generous in size than other hawker stalls offer. ‚òïüçπü•õ

Usually get the iced kopi, which is just nice! I can warmly recommend getting drinks from here while enjoying the food from the neighboring stalls.
Nasi Lemak is not bad, rice is not that fragrant but they do have 2 pieces of chicken wings.

Taste wise = okay.
Service = bad bad bad (4 Jan 2025 @7pm)
